description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experienced Mental Health Support Workers&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a number of Senior Mental Health Support Workers to work within the Crisis team in Portsmouth and the surrounding area.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will be to support trained practitioners in supporting patients at home and the community, patients who are in the acute phase of a mental illness and in crisis. This role will assist in the delivery of high standards of care to individual clients under the direction of a qualified nurse, occupational therapist or social worker.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a experienced support workers whoare dedicated to making a difference to patients in the community. Candidates should be&lt;span&gt;able to manage their own caseload effectively, able to make clear documentation whilst working autonomously in the community or in a team. You must be empathetic to others and able to effectively escalate risk. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate must be available to work shifts covering a 24 hour seven day a week service, this is a full time opportunity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Please outline in your application how you meet the criteria outlined in the job description and person specification.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You must be a car driver and have access to a vehicle for work purposes&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Further details about this role can be found in the accompanying job description and person specification.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We recommend contacting us to find out more about this role. To find out more or to visit our team please contact Louise Norris on louise.norris@solent.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interviews will take place on 25th November and 4th December 2020.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that should this post attract sufficient interest, we may choose to close at an earlier date. We strongly suggest that you apply at an early stage.&lt;strong&gt;If we have not contacted you within four weeks of the closing date of this post, please presume that you have not been selected. &lt;/strong&gt;Candidates selected for interview will be contacted within 2-3 weeks; therefore you should check your emails regularly including junk mail folders.&lt;/p&gt;
